simplify(1) -- Simplifies fractions when you're too lazy to!
============================================================

## SYNOPSIS

`simplify` [<fraction> | <numerator> <denominator>]

## DESCRIPTION

Simplifies fractions. Fractions may be supplied as a <fraction> in the form numerator/denominator, or may be supplied with the <numerator> and <denominator> as separate arguments.

Output is always in the form numerator/denominator.
